===Pronunciation===

:gran' it

===Noun===
#A group of [[igneous]] and [[plutonic]] [[rock]]s composed primarily of [[feldspar]] and [[quartz]]. Usually contains one or more dark [[mineral]]s, which may be [[mica]], [[pyroxene]], or [[amphibole]]. Granite is quarried for building stone, road gravel, decorative stone, and [[tombstone]]s. Common colors are gray, white, pink, and yellow-brown.

